    <text id="F0056T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Taggart's brief note states that all is well and that it is unlikely he will come
                    home soon.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>
        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient">Tilly</name>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1863-03-18">March 18 1863 </date>
                        <name type="place">Camp at Miners Hill Va </name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Tilly </salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I have had a letter from home for some days now and am not certain that it has
                    not been <del hand="h1">over a month</del> answered. Will drop you a line before
                    going to bed this morning to let you know I am well and that there is nothing
                    new or important going on here which must be my excuse for not writing a longer
                    letter. I received <orig reg="Lizzie's">Lizzies</orig> of the and <orig
                        reg="John's">Johns</orig> of the 16<hi rend="super">th</hi> today and will
                    answer them soon. From <orig reg="Lizzie's">Lizzies</orig> I learn that Fanny
                    Darragh is in Pittsburgh. I suppose<pb n="2"/> general conduct <unclear>
                        <orig reg="men">men</orig>
                    </unclear> if I should not participate in any of <unclear>the</unclear>. I may
                    get home some of these days but cannot state the <orig reg="precise"
                    >precis</orig> time. My love to all at home of course, including Fanny. </p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Your <abbr expan="Affectionate">Affect</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="Brother">Br</abbr>
                    </salute>
                    <signed>Bob </signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
